afloat by naive newcomers to the Internet, by the greedy brain-dead
and by inept corporate marketing people who insist on advertising
the fact that they haven't a clue when it comes to doing their jobs.

I'm not sure where this discussion can go from here, really. Let's
wrap it up now, unless you have a blinding insight that can make a
difference.

